# Visual Test Baselines

This directory contains baseline screenshots for visual regression testing.

## Structure

- `{example-id}-webgl2.png` - Baseline screenshot for WebGL2 backend
- `{example-id}-webgpu.png` - Baseline screenshot for WebGPU backend
- `diffs/` - Diff images when tests fail (not committed)

## Updating Baselines

To capture new baseline screenshots:

```bash
cd tests
UPDATE_BASELINES=true npx playwright test enhanced-functional-tests.spec.ts
```

## Notes

- Baselines are platform-specific (rendering may differ between OS)
- Update baselines after intentional visual changes
- Review diff images in `diffs/` folder when tests fail
